	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- I saw Q's CopperBars demo. I wonder if I could do something similar... The entire screen filled up with a colored pattern, then a centered (medium) square using color emphasis... that could be moved using the D-pad across the screen. Buttons A and B would toggle the emphasis mode.
<br />
<br />- Is this possible? I only see emphasis as BARS or half-screen... <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

