		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Doing it as a square in the middle of the screen would require some extremely precise timing, and you would NOT be able to give it per-pixel accuracy horizontally - even if you got it to stay perfectly still, the edges would still be rather jagged.
<br />
<br />Also, my demo is "Co<strong>p</strong>per Bars", not "Co<strong>o</strong>per Bars".

		

		</td>
